These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | cola | iced-tea   |
| Sport      | skiing    | cricket  | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, water
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, pakistani
1. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the dutch is on the far left##1
3. the dutch is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice     | water      |
| Nationality   | dutch | chinese | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: grapes, potato, strawberry
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | lemonade  | coffee       |
| Food       | grapes     | potato | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cherry, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, video-games
1. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | pear    | cherry     | cucumber |
| Hobby   | video-games | fishing | skydiving     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, goldfish
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | fish | turtle     | goldfish |
| Transport   | bike        | jet-ski | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, pepper, watermelon
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, subway
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating watermelon is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | watermelon | grapefruit      | pepper  |
| Transport   | quad-bike       | bus | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, electronic, hip-hop
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, lizard
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of electronic is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | soul     | electronic    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | lizard | mouse |

 #################################

 
