.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, western, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | iced-tea    | almond-milk    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | animation | documentary |

