The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, country
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | tea | fanta  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | country   | electronic |

