2. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | cabbage | artichoke   | cauliflower        |
| Sport   | cycling    | lacrosse | badminton |

