.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, onion, apricot
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person eating onion is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | apricot | cucumber       | onion  |
| Sport   | badminton  | handball | lacrosse |

 